Project Identity:
- Name: ClassiCode
- Tagline: Enterprise code classification preventing leakage before it happens
- Category: Security & Compliance
- Description: ClassiCode enforces mandatory file classification 
  (Confidential, Personal, Public, Internal), prevents unauthorized data leakage, 
  and provides tamper-evident audit trails for enterprise compliance.